---
title: Plant-Based Gouda Beyond Burger™ Made for Meat Lovers; Made from Plants
description: There are a lot of burger recipes out there, we know. Believe us when we say: this one truly goes above and beyond! Delicious Beyond Burger plant-based patties are topped with melty gouda cheese, jammy balsamic onions, tangy ketchup, and a creamy, Dijon-spiked aioli. Yeah, these bodacious burgers are sure to satisfy meat lovers and vegetarians alike (hello, 20g of plant protein!). Oh, and all of this goodness comes with crispy potato wedges and pickle spears on the side. That’s a lot to love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e25fed72ae33135333fad5e-e69e1d4c.jpg
